        "created_at": "2019-03-08T00:48:24.000Z",
        "cooked": "<ul>\n<li>\n<a href=\"https://www.cellartracker.com/wine.asp?iWine=1575378\"><strong>2011 Domaine Harmand-Geoffroy Gevrey-Chambertin 1er Cru Lavaux St. Jacques</strong></a> <em>- France, Burgundy, C\u00f4te de Nuits, Gevrey-Chambertin 1er Cru (3/5/2019)</em><br>\nThe nose is quite smoky, with some floral spice and red fruits thrown in for good measure. It is mid-weight, nicely balanced and has plenty of meat and earth savoury nuance. It is drinking nicely right now.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><em>Posted from <a href=\"https://www.cellartracker.com\">CellarTracker</a></em></p>",
